Name: 青蛙跳模拟器
About the game: This is a frog jumping game The little frog has poor eyesight and leads the little frog to jump from one leaf to another, which will give you time. Time is wealth, you can use your accumulated time as your own wealth, or you can contribute unselfishly. The time contributed by all players will be aggregated into a total time in real time. This total time will pass with the real world time. When this total time is 0, the game world will be reset.
